# Keep the build context small + reproducible: send source, gradlew, and gradle config —
# NOT build outputs, node_modules, caches, or VCS. (BuildKit reads this file automatically when
# the Dockerfile is deploy/Dockerfile. If your Docker is old, copy this to a root .dockerignore.)
.git
.gradle
**/.gradle
build
**/build
server/webui/node_modules
server/webui/dist
**/node_modules
*.log
.idea
.vscode
